<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<layout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools">

    <data>
        <variable
            name="vm"
            type="com.lakue.oburie.ui.myresume.upload.detail.ResumeUploadDetailViewModel" />
        <variable
            name="activity"
            type="com.lakue.oburie.ui.myresume.upload.detail.ResumeUploadDetailActivity" />
    </data>

    <LinearLayout
        android:orientation="vertical"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent">

        <include
            android:id="@+id/include"
            app:headTitle="@{@string/upload_detail_profile}"
            layout="@layout/include_header"
            app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf="parent"
            app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"
            app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"/>

        <androidx.core.widget.NestedScrollView
            android:layout_weight="1"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content">

            <LinearLayout
                android:orientation="vertical"
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content">

                <LinearLayout
                    android:paddingTop="16dp"
                    android:paddingLeft="20dp"
                    android:paddingRight="20dp"
                    android:paddingBottom="28dp"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content">

                    <TextView
                        android:textSize="14dp"
                        android:text="경력을 작성해주세요"
                        android:textColor="@color/color_dark_ffffff_000000"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/applesdgothicneob"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>

                    <EditText
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginTop="16dp"
                        android:background="@drawable/background_round_5_stroek_dddddd"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/applesdgothicneol"
                        android:gravity="top"
                        android:hint="경력\n
- 5년\n
\n
세부장르\n
✅ 결혼식\n
✅ 돌잔치\n
✅ 어린이행사\n
✅ 각종 축제 등 모든행사\n
\n
❗️진행스타일 \n
  -밝음\n
 -차분함\n
 -센스있다\n
 -재미있다\n
 -차분하다\n
\n
출연 경력\n
🏴‍☠️ W홈쇼핑 쇼호스트 출연\n
🏴‍☠️ 티몬 라이브 쇼호스트 출여\n"
                        android:minHeight="400dp"
                        android:paddingLeft="8dp"
                        android:paddingTop="12dp"
                        android:paddingRight="8dp"
                        android:paddingBottom="12dp"
                        android:textColor="@color/color_dark_ffffff_000000"
                        android:textSize="14dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_marginTop="24dp"
                        android:textSize="14dp"
                        android:text="수상내역을 자랑하세요."
                        android:textColor="@color/color_dark_ffffff_000000"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/applesdgothicneob"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>

                    <EditText
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginTop="16dp"
                        android:background="@drawable/background_round_5_stroek_dddddd"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/applesdgothicneol"
                        android:gravity="top"
                        android:hint="- 쇼핑 쇼호스트\n
\n
- 경희대 언론정보대학원 석사 과정\n
\n
- 티몬 라이브쇼호스트\n
\n
- 2019패럴스마트폰 영화제 시상식. mc\n
\n
- 2019쥴리스발레 페스티벌 mc\n
\n
- ksp add 기업행사 mc\n
\n
- 몬스터이벤트 mc팀장\n
\n
- GD컨벤션 예식 전속 사회자\n
\n
- 구리 스칼라티움 예식 전속 사회자\n
\n
- 파티움하우스 전속 사회자\n
\n
- 엔젤스데이 돌잔치 전속 사회자\n
\n
- 시각장애인 협회 도전골든벨 mc\n
\n
- 더존pn 기업행사 mc 등등.."
                        android:minHeight="400dp"
                        android:paddingLeft="8dp"
                        android:paddingTop="12dp"
                        android:paddingRight="8dp"
                        android:paddingBottom="12dp"
                        android:textColor="@color/color_dark_ffffff_000000"
                        android:textSize="14dp" />

                </LinearLayout>



            </LinearLayout>


        </androidx.core.widget.NestedScrollView>

        <LinearLayout
            android:backgroundTint="@color/color_dark_000000_ffffff"
            android:paddingTop="8dp"
            android:paddingBottom="8dp"
            android:paddingLeft="16dp"
            android:paddingRight="16dp"
            android:background="@color/white"
            android:orientation="horizontal"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content">

            <TextView
                android:foreground="@drawable/ripple_action"
                style="@style/BottomCompleteButton"
                android:text="@string/regist"/>

        </LinearLayout>

    </LinearLayout>

</layout>
